</blockquote>
<h2>Step 4: Add Search Volume, Keyword Difficulty, and CPC Data</h2>
<p>Now the template gets its fuel. You need 3 numbers on every row: search volume, keyword difficulty, and CPC.</p>
<p>Pull them in bulk, not one at a time. Ahrefs, Semrush, and Moz all accept CSV uploads of up to 10,000 keywords per bulk export. Paste column A into the tool, export the result, and VLOOKUP the data back into your template. A 3,000-keyword template takes 12 minutes to populate this way.</p>
